body:
Ponder Your Orbs is a small mod that adds in new orbs of origin based on every layer that is registered in the game.

 

By default these orbs will spawn in end city chests, however, this can be disabled in the `config/ponder_your_orbs_server.json` file, with the following text:
```json
{
  "ponder_your_orbs": {
    "spawn_in_end_city": false
  }
}
```
